OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBiden 'not told for days   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdefence chief in hospital' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Biden administration was not told  
OL,6, for days that US Defence Secretary     
OL,7, Lloyd Austin had been hospitalised, at 
OL,8, least one official has told US media.  
OL,10,FMr Austin, 70, was admitted to the     
OL,11,FWalter Reed Medical Center on Monday   
OL,12,Fdue to complications following surgery.
OL,14,FAn official told the BBC's US partner  
OL,15,FCBS that the White House was not       
OL,16,Finformed of this until at least        
OL,17,FThursday morning.                      
OL,19,FMr Austin has accepted responsibility  
OL,20,Ffor the lack of communication.         
